Package: fitnesslandscapes2
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Fitness Landscapes Version 2.0
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: c( person("Max", "Gotts", role = c("aut", "cre"), email =
          "mgotts@princeton.edu"), person("Lost Years Institute", role="cph", email="mg@lostyearsinstitute.org") )
Author: Max Gotts [aut, cre], Lost Years Institute [cph]
Date/Publication: 2021-27-06
Maintainer: Max Gotts <mgotts@princeton.edu>
Repository: CRAN
Maintainer: Max Gotts <mgotts@princeton.edu>
Description: Methods to make interacting with fitness/adaptive landscapes
    easier and more pleasant. Specifically set up to progrommatically perform
    projection pursuit regression, principal component analysis, linear discriminant analysis, create
    thin plate spline interpolated fitness landscapes, density surfaces
    (smoothed 3D histograms) and more.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
  stats,
  MASS,
  fields,
  plotly,
  dplyr
COPYRIGHTHOLDER: Max Gotts
